                        "id": "17995454084139976",
                        "text": "\ud83d\udea8 if you want to eat here, you\u2019ll want to make a reservation\ud83d\udea8\n\nHey foodies, if you\u2019re headed to Japan / Tokyo, this is one for your bucket list. The first thing you need to know is that you need to book because this is reservations only and it can be tricky to book because it fills up quite quickly. I could really only get a booking for 2pm on the day I landed. There were no other spots available. Hence the bag checking and rushing to Yoyogi after landing in #hanedaairport \n\nSo check their social media for flavours, but the strawberry cr\u00e8me br\u00fbl\u00e9e was the one I got. And this was a beautiful desert. It\u2019s a stunner that took a bit of time to make, and had flaky delicate snow in it.\n\n\ud83d\udd25\ud83c\udf67\ud83c\uddef\ud83c\uddf5 \ud83d\udccd@azukitokouri #azukitokouri \n\n#japan #japanfood #japanfoodie #japanlocal #japandesserts #azukitokouri #sydneyfoodies #sydneyfood #tokyo #tokyofoodie #japanese #travel #melbournefood #kakigori #japantrip"
                    }
                }
            ]
